(10171,'Xiaomi Earphones Ring Iron Pro In-ear wired sports music earphones and headset','New Bee Selection',51,'/goods-img/f3d269a4-5317-4b30-b164-1311f6c1f058.jpg','/goods-img/f3d269a4-5317-4b30-b164-1311f6c1f058.jpg','Using dual dynamic + balanced iron three-unit sound / balanced natural sound high-fidelity graphene diaphragm / 25 processes of polishing / elastic matte wire Pro Xiaomi dynamic iron earphones The sky and earth that nurture all things are always conveying the release and combination of sounds. They are also the source of inspiration. The different sounds of birdsong, flowing water, thunder, and wind whistling blend with each other to play the true nature of nature together. Xiaomi Mi In-Ear Earphones Pro uses dual "dynamic" units + "dynamic iron" units, integrating the three units into the same earphone. The mellow bass of the dual "dynamic" makes the sound more solid and stable, and the addition of graphene materials makes the sound details richer. The treble of the "dynamic iron" is clear, stable and natural, and you can feel the true sound of the three-frequency balance. As the sound flows, it seems as if you are in nature, and hearing these details makes the sound move your heart from the beginning. Dual dynamic + dynamic iron, three units sound, hear more details In order to truly achieve the balance of high, medium and low frequencies, Xiaomi Mi In-Ear Earphones Pro has added dual "dynamic" units, with the large dynamic coil responsible for the low and medium frequencies, and the small dynamic coil responsible for the high frequencies. With the cooperation of the "dynamic iron" unit, the earphones have a deep low-frequency dive, a solid mid-frequency sound, and richer details of the high frequencies. Those just right sounds are heard in the ears and in the heart. The three frequencies are more balanced and the sound is more natural Most of the instruments and vocals we hear are in the mid- and low-frequency bands. In order to make this part of 